Page Content​We are driven by our passion to improve the quality of life for millions of people around the world. Besides offering value-added products that benefit customers, we seek to build a future of continuous innovation through customized solutions.Our portfolio covers a wide range of olefins, glycols and derivatives, polymers, methanol, ammonia and fertilisers, and aromatics and MTBE products . Besides ethylene and propylene, which are used as basic feedstock for other products, we also market intermediate products such as butanol including basic performance chemicals. We host a  network of distribution centres and distribution partners as well as tailor-made logistics solutions and packaging types. Through effective product delivery and product handling, we ensure that customers are able to reap the benefits of high value service and excellence.​Business SegmentsPOLYMERHigh Density PolyethyleneLinear Low Density PolyethyleneLow Density PolythyleneMETHANOLMethanol  AMMONIA & FERTILIZERSUreaAmmonia OLEFINS, GLYCOLS & DERIVATIVESOlefinsGlycolsDerivativesAROMATICS & MTBEParaxyleneBenzeneMTBE

























